---
title: Fire “Works” Bacon Burgers with Crispy Potatoes & a Pepita-Studded Salad
description: The phrase “flavor explosion” should not be taken lightly. When we use it, we mean it! So trust us when we say that once you take a bite of this bodacious creation, your taste buds will be lighting up like a pinball machine. Our chefs infused bold, punchy flavors into every single layer of this burger. Buttery brioche buns are filled with mustard seed and Fry seasoning-infused beef patties, jalapeño-flecked pepper jack cheese, juicy tomato, sliced onion, a smoky special sauce, and finally, chipotle brown sugar bacon. Talk about going out with a bang!
